videos.headline: LSU's Edwards-Helaire motors opening kickoff 77 yards
videos.description: LSU's Clyde Edwards-Helaire weaves through traffic and jets the opening kickoff 77 yards, setting up a 24-yard Cole Tracy field goal.

videos.headline: McCrae bursts to the edge for UCF TD
videos.description: UCF finds the end zone on its opening possession as Greg McCrae takes the handoff and speeds to the edge for a 25-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: LSU's Burrow throws pick-6, takes huge hit on 93-yard return
videos.description: LSU QB Joe Burrow is picked off by Brandon Moore who zips 93 yards for a UCF defensive TD. Burrow takes a big hit from Joey Connors on the return.

videos.headline: LSU's Burrow rainbows TD to Jefferson
videos.description: LSU's Joe Burrow sits on the pocket and lofts a pass to Justin Jefferson, who lays out and snags the 22-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: LSU CB Alexander ejected for throwing punch
videos.description: LSU cornerback Terrence Alexander is ejected from the game after punching UCF receiver Gabriel Davis.

videos.headline: LSU QB Burrow uncorks TD strike to Dillon
videos.description: Joe Burrow whips a pass over the middle to Derrick Dillon, who sheds a tackle and gallops up the sideline for a 49-yard LSU touchdown.

videos.headline: Burrow takes another big shot, UCF's Gibson ejected
videos.description: UCF DB Kyle Gibson is ejected from the game for targeting after a blow to the head of LSU QB Joe Burrow.

videos.headline: LSU' Burrow, Jefferson connect for 2nd TD
videos.description: Joe Burrow buys time and hits a wide-open Justin Jefferson for a 33-yard touchdown, their second scoring connection of the half.

videos.headline: LSU's Delpit becomes 3rd player ejected in Fiesta Bowl
videos.description: LSU DB Grant Delpit is ejected for targeting on a late hit to the head of UCF's Dredrick Snelson, the game's third ejection of the half.

videos.headline: UCF QB Mack drops dime for TD before halftime
videos.description: UCF pulls within 3 of LSU before the half as Darriel Mack Jr. delivers a perfect ball to Gabriel Davis for a 32-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: LSU's Burrow displays toughness, tosses 3 TDs in half
videos.description: LSU QB Joe Burrow bounces back from absorbing multiple big hits in the first half and throws for three touchdowns to give LSU a lead over UCF.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (LSU’s Burrow displays toughness, tosses 3 TDs in half) 2018/1/1 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Burrow zings 4th TD pass of game
videos.description: Joe Burrow unloads his fourth touchdown of the game on a 32-yard pass to Ja'Marr Chase to give LSU a 10-point lead over UCF.

videos.headline: Coach O smashes headset after UCF TD
videos.description: LSU head coach Ed Orgeron unleashes his frustration and spikes his headset following UCF's touchdown before halftime.

videos.headline: Jefferson muffs punt for LSU
videos.description: LSU's Justin Jefferson signals for a fair catch, but muffs the punt and gives UCF the ball deep in in Tiger territory.

videos.headline: LSU's Edwards-Helaire goes Beast Mode
videos.description: LSU RB Clyde Edwards-Helaire refuses to go down, carrying four UCF defenders on his back for a 15-yard gain.

videos.headline: LSU pick ends UCF's 25-game win streak
videos.description: JaCoby Stevens' interception seals LSU's Fiesta Bowl victory and snaps UCF's 25-game win streak.

videos.headline: Burrow hangs tough, tosses four TDs in LSU win
videos.description: Joe Burrow perseveres through a physical game and throws four touchdowns in LSU's 40-32 Fiesta Bowl win over UCF.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Burrow hangs tough, tosses 4 TD in LSU win) 2018/1/1 ESHEET SOTFULL
